This course is excellent! When I started the class I was a little apprehensive, but the methods to declutter are relatively simple and laid out in a way that lowered my "Stress-O-Meter" pretty quickly...and it was in the red when it comes to digital clutter!!

I really enjoyed the course and the format is was presented in. I viewed each segment, took a break from the course, and did the work.  The process and support to do the process was perfect.  Although I have a couple of glitches to figure out because of my own skill level in technology I do feel much more organized and confident that things are not going to "lost".  Thank you both.
